Archive details[edit]

!!! Make archive certificate when complete

This archive was compiled using the following methods:

  1. A list of subjects related to this quest was retrieved from previous iteration of this archival effort[1]
  2. Location data for quest areas was dumped using Mejrs' Cache Tool (see archive section below)[1]
  3. Content templates for NPCs and Items were generated[1]
  4. Content templates for locations with interactions were generated[1]
  5. Content templates for locations with no interactions were generated[1]
  6. Marstead's playthrough was used to document the standard path[2]
  7. A list of area for this quest was created (see section below)[3]
  8. Locations without any interactions were added to the interaction section to record the lack of thereof[4]
  9. The RS Wiki page for that quest was parsed for archival tasks[5]
  10. A list of subject extracted from this page was compared against the earlier location dump to ensure that nothing was missing[6]
  11. The video Tutorial Island-2021-04-08.avi (from manpaint's private archives) was parsed for non-standard quest interactions[7]
  12. !!! runelibris1-tutorial-island-2018-1-1.avi
  13. !!! Add interface images from runelibris1-tutorial-island-2018-1-1.avi
  14. !!! Investigate interface bug by looking at pre-mining rework youtube videos
  15. !!! Fill gaps by parsing in-game
  16. !!! Re-import data from template cache (see filesystem)
